edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp

Class JcompType

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.ivy.jcomp.JcompType

  • public abstract class JcompType
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a type from semantic resolution. Each type has a unique object, and two instances of the type will have the same object.
